title: SOLD OUT- After Dark featuring "Go"
short_description: SOLD OUT- Presented by the Evening Associates
list_description: SOLD OUT- Presented by the Evening Associates
description:
Experience Go, the second installment of The Modern Series, with special guides and late-night access. Check out live performances by Monakr and Mano. Be sure not to miss interactive performances from acclaimed theatrical ensemble, Collaboraction, while sampling complimentary appetizers and cocktails from the cash bar. Attendees must be 21+, and valid ID is required upon entry.

This event is hosted by the Evening Associates. Please use the Modern Wing entrance at 159 East Monroe Street.

Follow the Evening Associates on Facebook for the latest news on After Dark and other events.
